  <h2>Workflow and analysis identity</h2>
  <p>
    Beyond MicroExonator, my work uses reproducible workflow management, large-scale RNA-seq
    processing, and machine learning to study RNA regulation across tissues, cell types, and
    disease cohorts. I develop and maintain Snakemake pipelines that combine splicing quantification
    with sequence-based machine-learning models, integrated with family-based genetics for variant
    interpretation in neurodevelopmental disorders.
  </p>

